---
title: Italian Chicken Meatballs in Sauce with Buttery Penne
description: Our Italian baked chicken meatballs taste just like Nonna's, but only take a fraction of the time! The secret to these leaner meatballs is swapping ground beef for chicken and pairing them with a homemade tomato sauce that keeps the dish flavourful.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-poulet-en-sauce-a-litalienne-1f3dfc3d.jpg
